# Grading rubric for stdio tests

Functionality:
- Test basic file stream operations

  4  stdio-fopen
  4  stdio-fclose
  4  stdio-fread
  4  stdio-fwrite

- Test character I/O

  3  stdio-fgetc
  3  stdio-fputc
  3  stdio-ungetc

- Test string I/O

  4  stdio-fgets
  4  stdio-fputs

- Test formatted I/O

  5  stdio-fprintf
  5  stdio-fscanf
  4  stdio-sscanf

- Test positioning

  4  stdio-fseek
  4  stdio-ftell

- Test error handling

  3  stdio-feof
  3  stdio-ferror

- Test standard streams

  4  stdio-stdout
  4  stdio-stdin

- Test buffering behavior

  4  stdio-buffer
  4  stdio-linebuf
